            {
              "text": "Emily follows a loud sound band while Lila follows a sign that lead to a new area.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Soon they see they are not together and feel a very concern feeling.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily looks around but can not see Lila among the many people again.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
