              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily walks to the area and sees the child who happy and offer a good food from his hand.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "The child says his name is Sam and he like to help visitors find their way always.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily thanks Sam and asks if he knows a short way back to the door soon.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Sam points to a narrow street and says the way is easy if she keep a good steady pace.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
