              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "She feels comfort and thanks Sam for his help before she run toward the door quickly.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "When Emily arrive at the main door, she sees Lila wait near a big area again.",
