              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Lila is happy to see Emily and they hold each other before they buy some food later.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "A person who sells bread offers them a free part and they thank him very soon.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "The person explain that the market is build many years ago and still brings many people today.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily listens and learns that each area has its own story and special product today.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "She promises to return next year and explore more of the market product again.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "After the day ends, Emily and Lila walk home feeling happy and very good.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They talk about the people they met and the lessons they learned today.",
