              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily thinks that being separate from a person can be hard but also an opportunity to grow today.",
              "audioStart": 0,
              "audioEnd": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "If she not be good, she might have missed the chance to meet Sam today.",
